data.description: Tired of postage stamp sized yards? Take a look at this lovely 3 bdrm, 2 bath ranch on almost an acre of land. Formal living w/wood burning fireplace and family room are both spacious, eat-in kitchen. Lots of updates including , whole home water system, new well tank, all appliances stay, even the washer and dryer.  There is also nice sized 2-car garage with a workshop . Home is close to interstates, downtown, and the airport.
